column3: In of of the demon worlds that the Deity Emperor created、the demon that ruled the World of Greed。
With the ability to absorb human greed、she has great power when facing a greedy human。
The number of tails increases according to the greed of the opponent、until she becomes a might nine-tailed fox。
Chefei was an ancient chinese tyrant、夏の桀王の妃である桀妃（末喜）の中国語読み。
桀妃は放蕩によって夏王国を滅ぼした傾城の美女であり、妲己とほぼ同一のエピソードを持つ。
後に日本で玉藻前伝説が描かれた際に、妲己と並んで桀妃もまた白面金毛九尾の狐の化身とされた。
For the female fox that destroyed a country to rule over the World of Greed、this may be because of Hazama's sense of irony。
